column5: Heading down to sarnia tomorrow morning,,,,anyone know directions to the launch,,,,coming from London on the 402,,,thanks

Sarnia Bay Marina, across the street from Stokes by the Bay, awesome restaurant btw, miss going there on friday/sat nights, take the front st cut off, head south, make a right on exmouth, make a left on harbour rd, launch is on the left  great place to shore fish for salmon/steelhead as well
